    <body>
      <milestone n="225" facs="279" unit="page"/>
      <p id="KT269-kilavi"><lb n="10"/>[itu, talaimakaṉ ciṟaippuṟattāṉākat talaimakaḷ tōḻikkuc <lb n="11"/>colluvāḷāyc colliyatu.] <lb n="12"/>[kallāṭaṉār pāṭiyatu.]</p>
      <lg xml:id="KT269">
        <l><lb n="13"/>269. cēyāṟu ceṉṟu tuṇaiyari yacāvā</l>
        <l><lb n="14"/>tucāvunarp peṟiṉē naṉṟumaṟ ṟilla</l>
        <l><lb n="15"/>vayaccuṟā veṟinta puṇṭaṇin tentaiyu</l>
        <l><lb n="16"/>nīṉiṟap peruṅkaṭal pukkaṉaṉ yāyu</l>
        <l><lb n="17"/>muppai māṟi veṇṇeṟ ṟarīiya</l>
        <l><lb n="18"/>vuppuviḷai kaḻaṉi ceṉṟaṉa ḷataṉāṟ</l>
        <l><lb n="19"/>paṉiyirum parappiṟ cērppaṟ</l>
        <l><lb n="20"/>kiṉivari ṉeḷiya ḷeṉṉun tūtē.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
<lb n="21"/>(i-ḷ.):― cuṟāmīṉ pāynta puṇ· āṟit tantaiyumkaṭalil (mīṉ <lb n="22"/>vēṭṭaikkuc) ceṉṟaṉaṉ ; aṉṉaiyum· uppaik koṭuttu nel<lb n="23"/>laip peṟakkaruti uppuviḷaikaḻaṉiyiṭam ceṉṟaṉaḷ; ātaviṉ, cērp<lb n="24"/>paṟku ippōḻtu variṉ· eḷiyaḷāvāḷ· eṉṟukūṟum tūtākac, <lb n="25"/>cēymaiyuḷḷa āṟṟaikkuntu, utavikaḷ· ariyavātalaikkuṟittu <lb n="26"/>varuntātu, (uṭaṉpaṭṭuk)kēṭpāraippeṟiṉ nallatākum. (e-ṟu.)
      </p>
      <p>
<lb n="27"/>eṉavē, aṟṟanōkkum kuṟṟamuṭaiya kaḷaviṉtaṉmaiyai <lb n="28"/>uṇarttiṉāḷām.
      </p>
      <p>
<lb n="29"/>meyppāṭu ― iḷivaral. payaṉ ― varaivukaṭātal.
      </p>

      <milestone n="258" unit="page" facs="312"/>
      <p xml:id="KT320-kilavi"><lb n="7"/>[itu, alar añci āṟṟāḷ ākiya talaimakaḷ talaivaṉ kēṭpāṉ ākat<lb n="8"/> tōḻikkuk kūṟiyatu.]
   <lb n="9"/>[tumpīmōci kīraṉ pāṭiyatu]</p>
      <lg xml:id="KT320">
        <l><lb n="10"/>320. peruṅkaṭaṟ paratavar koṇmī ṉuṇaṅkali</l>
        <l><lb n="11"/>ṉaruṅkaḻi koṇṭa viṟaviṉ vāṭaloṭu</l>
        <l><lb n="12"/>nilavuniṟa veṇmaṇal pullap palavuṭa</l>
        <l><lb n="13"/>ṉekkartoṟum parikkun tuṟaivaṉō ṭorunā</l>
        <l><lb n="14"/>ṇakkatōr paḻiyu milamē pōtaviḻ</l>
        <l><lb n="15"/>poṉṉiṇar marīiya puḷḷimiḻ poṅkarp</l>
        <l><lb n="16"/>puṉṉaiyañ cēri yivvūr</l>
        <l><lb n="17"/>koṉṉalar tūṟṟuṅ koṭumai yāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <milestone n="306" unit="page" facs="358"/>
      <head><lb n="13"/>mullai.</head>
      <p xml:id="KT400-kilavi"><lb n="14"/>[itu, viṉaimuṟṟivanta talaimakaṉ tērppākaṉait talaiyaḷittatu.]
    <lb n="15"/>[pēyaṉār pāṭiyatu.]
  </p>
      <lg xml:id="KT400">
        <l><lb n="16"/>400. cēyāṟu cellā māyi ṉiṭariṉṟu</l>
        <l><lb n="17"/>kaṉaiik kāmam peruntōṭ keṉṟu</l>
        <l><lb n="18"/>naṉṟupurin teṇṇiya maṉattai yāki</l>
        <l><lb n="19"/>murampukaṇ ṇuṭaiya vēkik kaḷarik</l>
        <l><lb n="20"/>karampaip putuvaḻip paṭutta matiyuṭai</l>
        <l><lb n="21"/>valavō, yiṉṟu tantaṉai tērēr</l>
        <l><lb n="22"/>nōyuḻan tuṟaiviyai nalka lāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <p><lb n="23"/>(i-ḷ.):― cēymaiyuḷḷa vaḻiyaik kaṭantu cellōmāṉāl, <lb n="24"/>periya tōḷkaḷaiyuṭaiyāḷukkuk kāmam mikuntu (ataṉāl,) tuṉ<lb n="25"/>pam (uṇṭākum) eṉṟu, peritum virumpi niṉaitta maṉattiṉai <lb n="26"/>yāy, murampiṭam· uṭaiyumpaṭi ceṉṟu kaḷarayuṭaiya pāḻnilaṅ<lb n="27"/>kaḷiṟ putuvaḻiyai uṇṭākkiya aṟivuḷḷa pāka ! iṉṟu tēraik <lb n="28"/>koṇarntaṉai ; (ataṉāl,) aḻakiya nōvāl varuntittaṅkumavaḷai <lb n="29"/>yāṉ talaiyaḷittalāṉ, (avaṭku iṭar) ilatāyiṟṟu. — (e - ṟu.)
  </p>
      <p><pb n="307" facs="359"/><lb n="1"/>murampu - kallirali uyarntirukkum nilam. karampai – pāḻ<lb n="2"/>nilam. viṉaiyāḷaṉai vēlaiyiṟutiyiṟ pukaḻtaṉ marapātaliṉ, ‘mati<lb n="3"/>yuṭai......tēr’ eṉṟuṉ. iṭar - mīṇṭuṅkoḷḷappaṭṭatu.
  </p>
      <p><lb n="4"/>meyppāṭu ― perumitam. payaṉ ― pākaṉait talaiyaḷittal.
  </p>
